Method Path Description GET /v1/nodes/status Get the status of all nodes GET /v1/nodes/{uid}/status Get a node&rsquo;s status Get all node statuses GET /v1/nodes/status Gets the status of all nodes. Includes each node&rsquo;s hostname and role in the cluster:
Primary nodes return &quot;role&quot;: &quot;master&quot;
Replica nodes return &quot;role&quot;: &quot;slave&quot;
Required permissions Permission name view_node_info Request Example HTTP request GET /nodes/status Request headers Key Value Description Host cnm.cluster.fqdn Domain name Accept application/json Accepted media type Response For each node in the cluster, returns a JSON object that contains the node&rsquo;s hostname and role.
